text: Olga Ahtinen (born 15 August 1997) is a Finnish footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Finland women's national team. ==Career== Ahtinen has been capped for the Finland national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish women's footballers Category:Finland women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Damallsvenskan players Category:IF Limhamn Bunkeflo players Category:Brøndby IF (women) players Category:Kokkola Futis 10 players Category:Pallokissat players
